=== 評價 ===
電影收穫普遍影評人的混合評論。根據[[爛蕃茄|爛蕃茄]]上收集的280篇專業影評文章，其中182篇給出了「新鮮」的正面評價，「新鮮度」為65%，平均得分6.1分（滿分10分）<ref>{{cite web|title='Quantum of Solace'|publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/quantum_of_solace/|accessdate=2012-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150612100937/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/quantum_of_solace/|archive-date=2015-06-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而基於另一影評網站[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上的48篇評論文章，其中24篇予以好評，2篇差評，22篇褒貶不一，平均分為58（滿分100）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/film/titles/quantumofsolace|title=Quantum of Solace|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2011-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100402105432/http://www.metacritic.com/film/titles/quantumofsolace|archive-date=2010-04-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
该片首映日[[票房|票房]]达到490万[[英镑|英镑]]（约800万美元），打破了英国电影首映日票房纪录<ref>{{cite news | language = en | author = ARCHIE THOMAS | url = http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117995122.html?categoryid=13&cs=1 | title = 'Solace' makes quantum leap in U.K. | publisher = VIRIETY | date = 2008-11-01 | accessdate = 2010-07-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100619060345/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117995122.html?categoryid=13&cs=1 | archive-date = 2010-06-19 | dead-url = no }}</ref>；首周累计票房1550万英镑（合2500万美元），打破了之前由《[[哈利·波特与火焰杯|哈利·波特与火焰杯]]》保持的1490万英镑的票房周纪录。

在[[中国大陆|中国大陆]]，该片首周票房超过6600万元[[人民币|人民币]]（约合970万美元）<ref>{{cite news | language = zh-hans | author = 张文泊 | url = http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/f/2008-11-11/10362244779.shtml | title = 《量子危机》首周6600万 创历史同期最好成绩 | publisher = 新浪娱乐 | date = 2008-11-11 | accessdate = 2010-07-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120119103218/http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/f/2008-11-11/10362244779.shtml | archive-date = 2012-01-19 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，创造了中国电影市场11月份的历史同期最好成绩。

该片在[[北美|北美]]上映后，首周票房达到7040万美元，远远超过上部007影片的票房成绩。

=== 榮譽 ===
《007量子危機》在{{link-en|第13屆衛星獎|13th Satellite Awards}}中，入圍最佳原創配樂、原創歌曲、視覺效果、電影與音效剪輯獎，且最終榮獲最佳原創歌曲獎<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pressacademy.com/satawards/awards2008.shtml|title=2008 13th Annual SATELLITE Awards|publisher=[[國際記者協會|International Press Academy]]|accessdate=2008-12-15|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081209100353/http://www.pressacademy.com/satawards/awards2008.shtml|archivedate=2008-12-09}}</ref>。電影還在{{link-en|第14屆評論家選擇獎|14th Critics' Choice Awards}}上獲提名至最佳動作電影<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117997072.html |author=Dade Hayes|title=Critics Choice favors 'Milk,' 'Button'|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|date=2008-12-09|accessdate=2008-12-09}}</ref>。而在{{link-en|第14屆帝國獎|14th Empire Awards|帝國獎}}方面，經由公眾投票，該片共奪下[[帝國獎最佳男主角|最佳男主角]]、[[帝國獎最佳女主角|女主角]]、新人、驚悚電影及配樂的提名<ref>{{cite news|title=Empire Awards nominate 'Quantum of Solace' five times, vote now online|publisher={{link-en|MI6-HQ.com|MI6-HQ.com}}|date=2009-03-02|url=http://www.mi6-hq.com/news/index.php?itemid=7396&t=mi6&s=news|accessdate=2009-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110511201330/http://www.mi6-hq.com/news/index.php?itemid=7396&t=mi6&s=news|archive-date=2011-05-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

